  "shareUrn": "urn:li:share:7012387897592926208",
  "text": "A few days ago I’ve got this gift from STRV’s awesome Norbert 🎁\n\nWhen I started my little business approx 3 years ago, I wouldn’t even believe that one day such successful houses like STRV would be my clients. Now they’re my fans and root for me like this!\n\nFor me, this is quite touching. It reminds me how my impostor syndrome blurs my vision. It reminds me that, at least from time to time, I should stop hustling, have a pause, and look back at what I’ve already built. And I should be content and happy. Thank you so much for this reminder, Noro! ❤️\n\nI wish you all to have such lovely customers, who are also your fans. Who will remind you that despite all your insecurities, you are actually awesome. And who will, perhaps even accidentally, remind you about it when you need it the most. Merry Christmas 🎄",
